  <brief_title>Perioperative Changes of Heart Rate Variability Related to Anxiety and Depressiveness in Patients Undergoing General Anesthesia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Perioperative Changes of Heart Rate Variability Related to Anxiety and Depressiveness in Psychologically Normal Patients Undergoing General Anesthesia</official_title>
